&nbsp;
This will be the first time a former president is charged in a criminal trial. The courtroom will become the new political stage of tycoon, which aims to transform the process into an electoral manifesto > to convince Americans to make donations and help him win as eight years ago. Trump will return to relaunch his accusations about the "electoral interference," "fairy trial" and declare himself a victim of the conspiracy of the Democrats. With good peace of the Americans, the process will not be broadcast on television and this is because the New York law prohibits it.
